														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2076346">
									

<p>Ok, I remember you saying that Aldon is TG, but can you elaborate further? Like, is she a shapeshifter what gets stuck in the male setting most of the time, or just a regular person who 1) knows about the Wanderer's Library, and 2) wants to be the opposite biological sex? Or am I being narrow-minded and missing a third possibility?</p>
<p>Anyway, neat stories so far, I hope you can keep it up!</p>
<p>Edit: By &quot;TG,&quot; I meant transgender (I've seen it abbreviated that way before), and I apologize for the confusion.</p>

