<blockquote>
<p>Ok, I remember you saying that Aldon is TG</p>
</blockquote>
<p>Not sure what you mean by that. I mean, she's my character, but if you're referring to a possible &quot;author avatar&quot; that'd be Navarro as he's the one I've written up a bio for on my author page.</p>
<p>Aldon is a totally normal baseline human who happens to have found the Wanderer's Library at some point. I haven't explored her discovery of it, but she's been a Wanderer for a couple years by this point. And yes, she's MTF trangender- she is physically, biologically male but she identifies as female.</p>

