			<div class="content" id="post-content-2183883">
									

<p>Not a whole lot beyond general descriptors, honestly. I haven't included much because I feel like it breaks flow randomly pointing it out since they're already familiar with each other, and it's not <em>that</em> important so I just leave it open a bit. Plus I'm not one for describing faces. What I do know is-</p>
<p>Jakeob Aldon is of Polish descent, which is important to me for some reason. 5'11&quot; (1.8034&#160;m), she looks fairly androgynous save for her man-hands. While I know she's dirty blonde I haven't figured out how she'd wear it. Probably kinda short. Uh. People have eyes. Blue-gray.</p>
<p>Finnegan is of Irish descent, because Finnegan is an Irish name. 6' (1.8288&#160;m), bit of a lanky dude. Chronically looks like he's half asleep or bored despite obvious evidence otherwise. Red hair cut short, good beard. Black beret always and forever, headphones often. Green eyes.</p>

